About

Tom Golisano is a 82 year old American Business Professional born on 14th November, 1941 in Rochester, New York, United States. His zodiac sign is Scorpio

Monica Seles is a 50 year old Hungarian Tennis Player. Born Monika Seles on 2nd December, 1973 in Novi Sad, Serbia, she is famous for Youngest French Open winner, Former nr. 1, was elected to the International Tennis Hall of Fame. Her zodiac sign is Sagittarius.
